483647/strip/true/crop/5100x1758+0+0/resize/400x138!/quality/90/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fewscripps-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F2e%2F4e%2F9e2805e04ebe8c2a7df576f40dc3%2Fwtkr-logo.png", "domain": "www.wtkr.com", "lang": "en", "author": "", "description": "At least a hundred teams competed in the Dulles Plane Day Pull at Dulles International Airport on Saturday to raise money for Special Olympics Virginia.", "keywords": ""}